summary: An FBI 302 report documenting a phone contact on January 13, 2021, with an individual (name redacted) who inquired about the return of her photographs provided to the FBI. The individual expressed upset over identifying as a victim, criticized Ghislaine Maxwell for not helping her or other girls, and stated Maxwell needed to take responsibility for her role with Jeffrey Epstein.
